| logical_plan  | Federated                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |  Sort: count(*) DESC NULLS FIRST                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |   Projection: hits.AdvEngineID, count(Int64(1)) AS count(*)                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |
|               |     Aggregate: groupBy=[[hits.AdvEngineID]], aggr=[[count(Int64(1))]]                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
